reviewText:
Kojak rocks !!!!!!
Terrific to watch shows from the past and this box set brings back good old memories. Enjoyed
every episode. Quality of dvd's  is new and flawless.
This box set is worth having.

We were not able to watch it.  A message came on the screen that we could not play it because of a region code.  The front and back cover was in French as well.  There was no package slip or return label.  I am disputing the charge.
